Package org.vanted.plugins.layout.stressminimization

A layout algorithm to Vanted that implements stress minimization.
Since:
2.8.0
Version:
1.0
Author:
David Boetius, Benjamin Halbritter, Thomas Komander, Silvan Reiner, Josua Sattler, Jakob Wietstock, Benjamin Moser
